_sText:
This is a map i made for the dodgeball mod, I know that Kat Fish created a nice addon for this (P.S Thanks Kit Kat) And I decided to make a map for it! This is one i made in about 1 hour its simple, but you have no weapons, and theres two sides, one for the T's and for CT's. People cannot cross over the line but the grenades can!

Enjoy This Map (Lots more coming)


http://addons.eventscripts.com/addons/view/dodgemod - Download Kit Kat's Dodgemod (Highly Recommended.)

http://addons.eventscripts.com/addons/view/NadeTrail - Download Nadetrails (Very useful for some nice effects on your grenades.)

http://addons.eventscripts.com/addons/view/DeathSounds - Really Fun To Have While dodgemod (funny death sounds when you die =D)
